quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  24,1,"(Wannan) sũra ce. Mun saukar da ita, kuma Mun wajabta ta, kuma Mun saukar da ãyõyi bayyanannu a cikinta, dõmin ku riƙa tunãwa.",""
  24,2,"Mazinãciya da mazinãci,<sup>1</sup> to, ku yi bũlãla ga kõwane ɗaya daga gare su, bũlãla ɗari. Kuma kada tausayi ya kãma ku game da su a cikin addinin Allah idan kun kasance kunã yin ĩmãni da Allah da Rãnar Lãhira. Kuma wani yankin jama, a daga mũminai, su halarci azãbarsu.","[1] Hukuncin waɗanda ba su yi aure ba ne, amma waɗanda suka yi aure hukuncinsu a jefe su har su mutu, bãyan sharuɗɗa sun cika, kamar yadda yake ga sunna. Kuma wannan ga hakkin 'ya'ya ne, amma bãyi, hukuncinsu bũlãla hamsin kawai."
  24,3,"Mazinãci bã ya aure<sup>1</sup> fãce da mazinãciya kõ mushirika, kuma mazinãciya bãbu mai aurenta fãce mazinãci kõ mushiriki. Kuma an haramta wannan a kan mũminai.","[1] Auren mazinãci kõ mazinãciya makarũhi ne ga wanda bahakanan yake ba, dõmin tsaron mutunci da kõre tuhuma."
  24,4,"Kuma waɗanda ke jĩfar<sup>1</sup> mãtã masu kãmun kai, sa'an nan kuma ba su jẽ da shaidu huɗu ba to, ku yi musu bũlãla, bũlãla tamãnin, kuma kada ku karɓi wata shaida tãsu, har abada. Waɗancan su ne fãsiƙai.","[1] Haddin ƙazafi bũlãla tamãnin ga ɗã, kõ arba'in ga bãwa idan ya yi ƙazafi ga ɗã,."
  24,5,"Fãce waɗanda suka tũbadaga bãyan wannan, kuma suka gyãru, to lalle ne Allah Mai gãfara ne, Mai jin ƙai.",""
  24,6,"Kuma waɗanda ke jĩfar mãtan<sup>1</sup> aurensu kuma waɗansu shaidu ba su kasance a gare su ba, fãce dai kansu, to, shaidar ɗayansu, shaida huɗu ce da Allah, 'Lalle shĩ, haƙĩƙa, yanã daga magasganta.'","[1] Hukuncin ranstuwar li'ani da yadda ake yin ta."
  24,7,"Kuma ta biyar cẽwa 'La'anar Allah ta tabbata a kansa, idan ya kasance daga maƙaryata.'",""
  24,8,"Kuma yanã tunkuɗe mata azãba ta yi shaida, shaida huɗu da Allah, 'Lalle shĩ haƙĩƙa, yanã daga maƙaryata.'",""
  24,9,"Kuma tã biyar cẽwa 'Hushin Allah ya tabbata a kanta idan ya kasance daga magasganta.'",""
  24,10,"Kuma bã dõmin falalar Allah ba a kanku, da rahamar Sa, kuma cẽwa Allah Mai karɓar tũba ne, Mai hikima!",""
